<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>3179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>8730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫约翰和妻子莫贝尔没什么钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夏天又热又干，他们的玉米快死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是莫贝尔想买辆新车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有足够的钱。”农夫约翰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以卖掉你的拖拉机。”莫贝尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要那辆拖拉机来耕地，莫贝尔。”农夫约翰说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们明年可能会买得起一辆新车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我现在就需要一辆新车！”莫贝尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”农夫约翰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都安静了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天色变晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要为明天的早餐准备鸡蛋。”莫贝尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我拿些鸡蛋过来，约翰。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫约翰走到外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在鸡圈里只有三个鸡蛋了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是其中一个与众不同。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”农夫约翰大喊起来，“莫贝尔！过来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莫贝尔走进鸡圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么，约翰？”她问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么大喊大叫？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得这个蛋是金子做的。”农夫约翰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起来给她看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”莫贝尔说，“真亮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在鸡圈墙壁上敲了敲蛋壳。没有碎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得没错，约翰。这是个金蛋。现在我们可以买辆好车了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得小心点儿，莫贝尔。”农夫约翰说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先进屋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莫贝尔和农夫约翰坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金蛋就放在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们先等到明天早上吧。”农夫约翰说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想看看鸡能不能再下一个金蛋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们上床睡觉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早上，在鸡圈里又多了一个金蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，约翰！”莫贝尔尖叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有了这只鸡，我们可以搬到更大的房子里去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抱起鸡来，亲了又亲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要成为百万富翁了，约翰！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”农夫约翰说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再过几天我们就会变得很有钱了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“约翰！”莫贝尔小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道怎么做，现在就能得到所有的金蛋！我们不需要等。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么做？”农夫约翰问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以杀掉这只鸡。”莫贝尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，我们就可以马上拿到所有的金蛋了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是农夫约翰杀掉了那只鸡，但是里面没有金蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”莫贝尔尖叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“金蛋去哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们本来应该等的。”农夫约翰说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们再也得不到金蛋了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莫贝尔开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们永远都成不了百万富翁了。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么坏事会发生在我们身上？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坏事的发生是因为人们太贪心了。”农夫约翰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>